00:32:15.020 --> 00:32:19.420
First, wash the rice three times to take off any extra starch. 

00:32:22.460 --> 00:32:24.060
Melt butter in a pan. 

00:32:26.260 --> 00:32:28.180
Add four big spoons of orzo. 

00:32:30.100 --> 00:32:34.180
